Ross Barkley on season restarting:<br />
<br />
&quot;It was frustrating because I was in good form. I was getting a decent run in the side and things were going well, for the team as well because we were getting the results that we needed and we were kicking on.&quot;

Lampard on Selection problems:&quot;It's a nice problem, we have missed big players. Loftus-Cheek and Kante at times. We are going to need everyone in the squad. The five subs is a good thing and the bigger bench should stay the course.<br />
<br />
To get the younger players involved, it is a good thing.&quot;
